{"tid":615081,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識brake 同呔？","createTime":"2018-04-03T05:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T10:31:02.000Z","uid":167560,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9d1e9179528a91d657477d7343fa0e63ba832a","tid":615081,"uid":167560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"架車買左冇耐 仲慢慢摸緊 尋日上左山走轉試下手感<br />\n發覺每次入灣前由120km+重brake 四條呔會響曬 <br />\n然後成架車向前滑 有d似冇ABS lock呔咁 (冇著abs light)<br />\n完全收唔到<br />\n上手車主裝左套toyo proxes 4 all season<br />\n乾地入灣快少少都似想炒咁 濕地仲廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁應該係呔問題定abs?"},{"pid":"94525b9b4619807eaf8c9903055311e35c8921db","tid":615081,"uid":74171,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"好明顯係人嘅問題"},{"pid":"b65b74c0e52bd59aa979e862fdd416639a3b2999","tid":615081,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"條呔仲有無坑"},{"pid":"fd38456ed02424e78980362e75f95a5984753e00","tid":615081,"uid":81270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:47:34.000Z","msg":"咩款，有冇改你都冇講。<br />\n<br />\n四呔響姐係你brake 冇問題，只係落大咗，最後四條呔s 冇曬摩擦力。<br />\n<br />\n建議係換呔/or <br />\n<br />\n不斷試個呔摩擦臨界點係邊，由重brake 到輕brake ,試到唔會推唯止/or<br />\n<br />\n換架有abs 嘅車"},{"pid":"bdfcb71fbb3918f690d2ff542bb066648f78ee3c","tid":615081,"uid":167560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b65b74c0e52bd59aa979e862fdd416639a3b2999","tid":615081,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"條呔仲有無坑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"仲有至少60%以上"},{"pid":"4289b9a945b533ea440dde5a4a4b6087fdb687c7","tid":615081,"uid":7674,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"講真，120衝到入灣前先重dup<br />\n你買乜呔都響架啦<br />\n玩壞左個abs或者abs救唔切你就咁拜拜<br />\n你真係以為abs萬能保平安呀？"},{"pid":"ef63b7c70079efd7100ef3e1e56bc411e99c0172","tid":615081,"uid":